        "message": "LU-11435 mdt: check lock contention for MDT IO locks\n\nCheck lock contention in mdt_brw_enqueue() and report it\nto the client, so later may use lockless IO, restore lost\n'lockless_truncate' paramenter in mdc and add related\ntests in sanityn.sh (32c and 32d)\n\nSigned-off-by: Mikhail Pershin <mpershin@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ia6d042141419df147e8192e32489f30df407b37f\n"
